<br>
What's that? You don't know what a Blog is? Well my friend, a Blog is a &quot;Weblog&quot; or &quot;Online Journal&quot;.<br>
<br>
You can find Burma's Blog at his website, <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.bubbafilmsstudios.com">www.bubbafilmsstudios.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
